titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on 1H-Imidazole-4,5-dimethanol, 2-phenyl- (9Cl).

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 6/6/2006--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on 1H-Imidazole-4,5-dimethanol, 2-phenyl- (9Cl).
